  "text": "Being a proliferation of the normal cells of the breast, fibroadenomas may suffer the same changes such as breast parenchyma, including the development of malignancy. The literature data is limited regarding the correlation of these two entities, with a reported incidence between 0.125% and 0.02% [CITATION_1] .",
